                     <interp inst="t17760710-31-verdict145" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               GUILTY of stealing to the value of ten-pence
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
